title: Lynx, Fever ready for WNBA Finals-deciding Game 5
text:
> Indiana Lynx, Fever ready for WNBA Finals-deciding Game 5 Minnesota Lynx's Renee Montgomery holds out her arms in the first half of Game 4 of the WNBA Finals basketball series, in Indianapolis against the Indiana Fever, Sunday, Oct. 11, 2015. (AP Photo/Michael Conroy)
